section.def:
Board
                (委員會) means the Medical Laboratory Technologists
            Board established under section 5 of the Ordinance;

examination
                (考試) means an examination held in pursuance of
                section 15A of the Ordinance;

subparagraph.content:
a registered dentist as defined by section 2(1) of the
                        Dentists Registration Ordinance (Cap. 156);
                        or

subsection.def:
CMHHK technologist (香港中醫醫院化驗師) means a medical laboratory technologist
                who is authorized by The Chinese Medicine Hospital of Hong Kong to provide services
                to a CMHHK patient;

paragraph.content:
in a case where the complaint is that the respondent has been guilty of
                    misconduct, state in the form of a charge, which shall be formulated by the
                    Secretary, the matters into which inquiry is to be held;

section.def:
order
                (命令) means an order made by the Board in the
            exercise of its powers under section 22 of the Ordinance;
